00:29:13.020 --> 00:29:14.130 align:middle line:90%
>>MOODY: Oh, great.

00:29:14.130 --> 00:29:18.180 align:middle line:10%
How about RaymondMoodyNDE.com

00:29:18.180 --> 00:29:19.940 align:middle line:10%
>>NOORY: N-D-E. Perfect.

00:29:19.940 --> 00:29:22.402 align:middle line:10%
>>MOODY: Or LifeAfterLife.com.

00:29:22.402 --> 00:29:24.110 align:middle line:10%
>>NOORY: See, you're
