We could talk for hours.

00:29:41.684 --> 00:29:42.850 align:middle line:90%
>>MOODY: We could, we could.

00:29:42.850 --> 00:29:43.910 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: About just life.

00:29:43.910 --> 00:29:44.510 align:middle line:90%
>>MOODY: That's right.

00:29:44.510 --> 00:29:46.509 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Thank you for
